  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Wake Cup is a caffeinated non-violent tower defense & clicker mash-up with rogue-lite meta progression.      </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We need you, barista! Wake up and fight against the exhausted masses and keep them energised with a cup of coffee. The economy must flow!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881430/extras/3cba6bc6f2f2e14221fd53bdb96afeff.poster.avif?t=1772722856\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881430/extras/3cba6bc6f2f2e14221fd53bdb96afeff.webm?t=1772722856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881430/extras/3cba6bc6f2f2e14221fd53bdb96afeff.mp4?t=1772722856\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build a resource chain to keep the coffee supplies running.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wake up, brew coffee, sell, collect likes, go viral, burn out and repeat! Failing and replaying levels is important to  get extra likes and improve your business with a variety of upgrades in the shop.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881430/extras/3a1a6f088a8f674552a6dc259455bbd1.poster.avif?t=1772722856\" width=616 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881430/extras/3a1a6f088a8f674552a6dc259455bbd1.webm?t=1772722856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881430/extras/3a1a6f088a8f674552a6dc259455bbd1.mp4?t=1772722856\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br>Enjoy two different ways to play the game with a dozen of standard levels and endless mode to test your survival skills and earn extra coins! How long can you make it before tasting the bitter defeat?  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881430/extras/5620166f3d0489d404c6ba8485a393a1.poster.avif?t=1772722856\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881430/extras/5620166f3d0489d404c6ba8485a393a1.webm?t=1772722856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881430/extras/5620166f3d0489d404c6ba8485a393a1.mp4?t=1772722856\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10+ Hours of playtime  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >60 Steam achievements to challenge yourself  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >12 Unique maps  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >9 Unique enemies     </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 Unique buildings with multiple upgrades each!  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >70+ Unlockable upgrades to customise your business </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 Power-up to enhance your strategy</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881430/extras/ab2a9bc990f821209f51b8b8866f6c14.poster.avif?t=1772722856\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881430/extras/ab2a9bc990f821209f51b8b8866f6c14.webm?t=1772722856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881430/extras/ab2a9bc990f821209f51b8b8866f6c14.mp4?t=1772722856\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hatch cute Blobista eggs that pop on the maps and put them to work.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blobistas are cute and very efficient at helping you to speed up the workflow. Hatch them, put them at work and let them do their magic while you lay back and enjoy your growing coffee business. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881430/extras/0215b41a5766cf4e96530d04c46d96d3.poster.avif?t=1772722856\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881430/extras/0215b41a5766cf4e96530d04c46d96d3.webm?t=1772722856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881430/extras/0215b41a5766cf4e96530d04c46d96d3.mp4?t=1772722856\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br>  <br>  <br><strong>Stay energised. Much love,</strong> <br>  <br><strong>Pyralis Studio.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881430/extras/97764f46a2262af766261cc6365eb0cd.avif?t=1772722856\" width=250 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Wake Cup is a caffeinated non-violent tower defense & clicker mash-up with rogue-lite meta progression.      </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We need you, barista! Wake up and fight against the exhausted masses and keep them energised with a cup of coffee. The economy must flow!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881430/extras/3cba6bc6f2f2e14221fd53bdb96afeff.poster.avif?t=1772722856\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881430/extras/3cba6bc6f2f2e14221fd53bdb96afeff.webm?t=1772722856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881430/extras/3cba6bc6f2f2e14221fd53bdb96afeff.mp4?t=1772722856\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build a resource chain to keep the coffee supplies running.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wake up, brew coffee, sell, collect likes, go viral, burn out and repeat! Failing and replaying levels is important to  get extra likes and improve your business with a variety of upgrades in the shop.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881430/extras/3a1a6f088a8f674552a6dc259455bbd1.poster.avif?t=1772722856\" width=616 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881430/extras/3a1a6f088a8f674552a6dc259455bbd1.webm?t=1772722856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881430/extras/3a1a6f088a8f674552